* Razmislim* malo o tome (I'll think about it a bit).
* Njegov odgovor me je uverio da treba da *razmislim* o tome (His answer convinced me to think about it). 
* *Razmislim* malo, moraš biti obazriv (Think carefully, you have to be careful). 
* Da *razmislim* da li je to istina? (Should I consider if that's true?). 
* *Razmislim* o njemu, on zaslužuje da se o njemu razmišlja (Think about him, he deserves to be thought of).